## Platform values to standardize on

| Platform | `platform` value |
|---|---|
| Linux RPM-based | `linux-rpm` |
| Linux Debian-based | `linux-deb` |
| Windows | `windows` |
| macOS | `macos` |

---

## How FastAPI queries this

Your app fetches `index.json` once (cache it), then filters in-memory:
```
GET /policies?application=apache              → all apache entries
GET /policies?application=apache&platform=linux-rpm  → apache RPM only
GET /policies?platform=windows                → all Windows policies
GET /policies/{id}                            → metadata for one policy
GET /policies/{id}/raw                        → proxies the raw YAML file
